description: Pristine two bedroom, one and one-half bathroom duplex unit in desirable east side location. This condo truly has it all... Central heat and a/c, gas fireplace, hardwood floors throughout, washer/dryer in-unit, convenient half-bath serving open living/dining area, two full sized bedrooms, granite kitchen with custom oak and maple cabinetry, custom center island, and recessed lighting with hand-selected pendant compliments. Additionally, This unit boasts two private outdoor spaces with storage. First, a convenient outdoor deck directly off of the kitchen gives a tremendous indoor/outdoor feel for cooking and entertaining. Second, a  LARGE fenced in back yard at ground level provides a welcome space for the family pet or child.
